title: Start
body:
One day, Mom asked Jenny to help her send food to her Grandma.

		Mom: Remember, you must come back home before 6pm, OK?

		Jenny: Sure, Mom.

		Mother: You have to be careful.

		Mother: Do not let the food spoil, do not play around and follow the road rules before crossing the road.

		Jenny: Ok, mom. I'll be back soon. Bye!
